f(k+1)=\frac 1 n + \frac{n-2}{n}f(k)
\frac 1 2
f(k+1)-\frac 1 2 = \frac{n-2}{n}(f(k)-\tfrac 1 2)
f(k) - \frac 1 2 = -\frac 1 2 \left(\frac{n-2}{n}\right)^{k}
f(n) = \frac 1 2 - \frac 1 2 \left(1-\frac 2 n\right)^n.
