25[1 - (24/25)^{50}] \approx 22
(49/50 + x/50)^{50} = \sum_{i=0}^{50} \binom{50}{i} (x/50)^i (49/50)^{50-i}
(49/50 - x/50)^{50} = \sum_{i=0}^{50} (-1)^i \binom{50}{i} (x/50)^i (49/50)^{50-i}
(49/50 + x/50)^{50} - (49/50 - x/50)^{50} = 2 \sum_{i \; odd} \binom{50}{i} (x/50)^i (49/50)^{50-i}
(49/50 + 1/50)^{50} - (49/50 - 1/50)^{50} = 2 \Pr(\text{i is odd})
\Pr(\text{i is odd}) \approx 0.43506
50 \cdot \Pr(\text{i is odd}) \approx 21.75
